how are you? 
 " (eh)   你好吗  (hp) nǐ hǎo ma 
 " (wpas) 你怎么样 (hp) nǐ zěnme yàng

thanks
  " (eh)   谢谢 (ep) xièxiè 
  " (wpas) 多谢 (ep) duōxiè

you're welcome
   " (eh) 不客气 (hp) bù kèqì
   " (wpas) 没事儿 (hp) méishì er

Can I order/have/get a coffee
    "  (eh) 我想单一一个咖啡 (hp) wǒ xiǎng dānyī yīgè kāfēi
    "  (eh)  来个咖啡     (hp) lái gè kāfēi

how much does this cost?
  " (eh) 这个多少钱 (hp) zhège duōshǎo qián 
  " (eh) 这个怎么卖 (hp) zhège zěnme mài (literally) how to sell this 

