  :: yes, no, negative :: 

 yes       (eh) 对呀     (hp) duì ya
 yes       (eh) 是的     (hp) shì de
  "        (note) There is no simple one to one translation for yes and no
 yes/right/correct (eh) 对   (hp) duì (e.g.) nǐ duì  (ph) 你对  (he) you are right

nǐ duì gōngzī mǎnyì ma  (ph) 你对工资满意吗  (he)  Are you satisfied with your salary?


 no        (eh) 不   (hp) bù
 no        (eh) 没有  (hp) méiyǒu
  "        (note) There is no simple one to one translation for yes and no

 no/no thanks i.e. I don't need it (eh) 不要 (hp) bù yào

 :: okay, ok, no worries, no problem ::

好啊  (ep) hǎo a   (pe) ok
没错  (hp) méi cuò (pe) Exactly! That's right i.e. not wrong
行   (hp) xíng   (pe) ok - in response to a suggestion
可以  (hp) kěyǐ    (pe) can do/sure/you may


no matter (eh)  méiguānxì  (hp) 没关系
méishì 'r (ph) 没事儿 (he) it's okay

it's nothing/it doesn't matter
               "      (eh) 没关系 (hp) méiguānxì

fine   (eh) 没事   (hp) méishì

okay, all right (eh) 好吧 (hp) hǎo ba 
 yěxǔ (ph) 也许 (he) maybe

  ####################################

  :: a bit, slightly ::


yīdiǎn (ph) 一点 (he) a bit - adjective
   " (e.g.) yīdiǎn kāfēi (ph) 一点咖啡 (he) a little coffee 

yǒudiǎn (ph) 有点 (he) a bit - adverb
  "  (e.g.) yǒudiǎn lèi (ph)  有点累 (he)   a little tired


