 :: order food, example episode, _sequence_ ::

wǒ huílái le (ph) 我回来了 (he) I'm back

hái hǎo ma (ph)  还好吗 (he) How u doing?

jīntiān de kè zěnme yàng (ph)  今天的课怎么样 (he) How was today's class?

hái kěyǐ (ph)  还可以 (he) Well enough

jiùshì yǒudiǎn lèi (ph)  就是有点累 (he) Just a little tiring

nǐ zuòle fàn ma (ph)  你做了饭吗 (he) Did you make any food?

méiyǒu, wǒ tài lèile (ph)  没有, 我太累了 (he) No, I'm too tired.

nà, wǒmen yīqǐ zuò ba (ph)  那, 我们一起做吧 (he) Then, let's cook together!

bùyào la                (ph)  不要啦      (he) Nooooo
wǒ zhēn de bùxiǎng dòng (ph)  我真的不想动 (he) I really don't want to move

hǎo ba, nà wǒmen diǎn shíwù ba (ph)  好吧, 那我们点食物吧 (he) Okay, then let's order something.

diǎn shénme ne (ph)  点什么呢 (he) What to order?

pīsà zěnme yàng (ph)  披萨怎么样 (he) How about pizza?

tài hǎo le. wó zuì ài chī pīsà (ph)   太好了. w哦最爱吃披萨 That's great! I love pizza the most!

hǎo zhǔyì (ph)  好主意 (he) Good idea! 

 -:: _sequence_ ::

