jǐ suì   (ph) 几岁  (he) how old
jǐ gè    (ph) 几个  (he) how many / as question
  " (e.g.) nǐmen xiǎodé zǔ yǒu jǐ gèrén (ph) 你们晓得组有几个人 (he) How many people are in the/your group

jǐ wèi   (ph) 几位 (he) several people/how many people
jǐ nián  (ph) 几年 (he) what year

