:: time | time concepts | early , late , before, after ::

now (eh) 现在 (hp) xiànzài
zhèng (ph) 正 (he) just
zhèngzài (ph) 正在  (he) just now, right now
then/just/at once/suddenly (eh) 就 (hp) jiù
tā gǎn gāng jìnle diàntī  (ph) 他敢刚进了电梯  (he) He just got into the elevator
just now  (eh) 刚才 (hp) gāngcái

tā gāng gēchàng de hěn hǎo (ph)  他刚歌唱的很好  (he) He just sang very well

tā chànggē chàng dé hěn hǎo (ph)  他唱歌唱得很好  (he) He sings very well


  ####################################

  :: grammar, rules ::

grammar (eh) 语法 (hp) yǔfǎ

adverbs with dé/dei (rule) x does-verb Y, does-verb dé/dei adverb
  "  (e.g.) tā wán fēipán, wán dé hǎobù hǎo  (ph) 他玩飞盘玩得好不好  (he) Is he good at playing Frisbee?
  "  (e.g.) tā xiàbān xià dé hěn wǎn (ph) 他下班下得很晚 (he) gets off work very late

using 不/bù versus  没有/méiyǒu (rule) 不/bù Negates in the Present and Future
   " (rule) 不/bù negates Habitual Actions (e.g.) 我 不 吃 肉 (hp) Wǒ bù chī ròu (pe) I don't eat meat
   " (rule) 不/bù is normally used with adjectives (e.g.) 我 家 不 远 (hp) Wǒ jiā bù yuǎn (pe) my home is not far
   " (rule) 不/bù Is for Asking Questions (e.g.) 她 想 不 想 来？ (hp) tā xiǎng bu xiǎnglái? (pe) does she want to come?
@meirule " (rule) 没/méi Negates Past Actions (e.g.) 你 没 去 上班 吗 ？ (hp) nǐ méi qù shàngbān ma? (pe) did you not go to work?
   " (rule) Only 没/méi Negates 有/yǒu
   " (rule) 没 méi Is for Making Comparisons
   " (rule) 不 bù Is Used Almost Exclusively with Certain Verbs

nǐ dài méi dài jiǎnlì (ph) 你带没带简历 (he) Did you bring your resume?

Wǒ jīntiān méiyǒu qù xuéxiào (ph) 我今天没有去学校 (he) I didn't go to school today
     " (e.g.) $meirule.1

wǒmen de yuángōng bù duō (ph) 我们的员工不多 (he)  we don't have many employees
nǐ méi huídá zhège wèntí  (ph) 你没回答这个问题  (he) you didn't answer the question

@bu I did not meet with him last weekend (eh)  上周末我没有见到他 (hp) shàng zhōumò wǒ méiyǒu jiàn dào tā 
      " (prop) WRONG: wǒ shàng gè zhōumò bù gēn tā jiànmiàn (ph) 我 上个 周末 不 跟 他 见面 (see) $bu.2

 :: grammar, use of shi as something like "I'm like"... :: 

wǒ shì zài yīngguó chūshēng de (ph)  我是在英国出生的 (he) I was born in England
    " (compare) wǒ chūshēng zài yīngguó  (ph) 我出生在英国 (he) I was born in England

tā bùshì zài yīngguó xué de wùlǐ (ph)  他不是在英国学的物理 (he) He didn't study physics in England. 

###############################################

   :: prefix yi patterns ::

 共 (hp) gòng (pe) altogether (e.g.) 一共 (hp) yīgòng (pe) altogether / in total

yīqǐ   (ph) 一起 (he) together
yǐjīng (ph) 已经 (he) already
yīdìng (ph) 一定 (he) must/definitely 
   "   (e.g.) tā yīdìng bù huì yuánliàng nǐ (ph) 他一定不会原谅你 (he) he certainly won't forgive you 

yǐqián (ph) 以前 (he) before
yǐhòu  (ph) 以后 (he) after
yībiān (ph) 一边 (he) at the same time / alongside

yībiàn (ph) 一遍 (he) once
   "   (e.g.) wǒmen zài tīng yībiàn ba  (ph)  我们再听一遍 吧 (he) let's listen to it again
   "   (sl) yībiān
   "   (!confuse) yībiān

yībān  (ph) 一般 (he) usually 

yīcì (ph) 一次 (he) once/once time

   "  (e.g.) qǐng zài jiǎnchá yīcì  (ph) 请再检查一次  (he) please check again

