  :: anymore, le ::
  
Wǒ bù chī yèxiāo (ph) 我不吃夜宵 (he) I don't eat midnight snacks

   " (e.g.) wǒ bù chī yèxiāo le (ph) 我不吃夜宵了 (he) I don't eat midnight snacks anymore

$PREV.2 (note) adding past "le" can mean not anymore

  ####################################

  :: no, not, didn't, won't ::

 méi (ph) 没 (he) negative not / none / have not etc
  "  (e.g.) wǒ méi qù    (ph) 我没去  (he) I didn't go ..
  "  (e.g.) wǒ méi qù guò (ph) 我没去过 (he) I haven't been ..
  "  (e.g.) wǒ méi qù nà jiā fànguǎn    (ph) 我没去那家饭馆  (he) I didn't go to that restaurant
  "  (e.g.) wǒ méi qùguò nà jiā fànguǎn (ph) 我没去过那家饭馆 (he) I've never been to that restaurant
  "  (see also) $meirule.1


méi yǒu (ph) 没有 (he) don't have
   " (contrast) méi yóu (ph) 没油 (he) no petrol


