####################################
# Patterns
####################################

  :: shi ::

shì (ph) 是 (he) to be / yes

  " (e.g.) wǒ shì (ph) 我是 (he) I am
  " (e.g.) shì de (ph) 是的 (he) yes

shí (ph) 时 (he) hour / time
 " (e.g.) shíjiān (ph) 时间 (he)  time
 " (e.g.) shíhòu (ph)  时候 (he)  during / time of
 " (e.g.) shídài (ph)  时代 (he)  era
 " (e.g.) xiǎoshí (ph)  小时 (he)  hour
 " (e.g.) tóngshí (ph)  同时 (he)  at the same time
 " (e.g.) dăngshí (ph)  当时 (he)  then/at that time
 " (e.g.) suíshí (ph)  随时 (he)  anytime
