      " (e.g.) nǐ língchén yīdiǎn cái huí jiā (ph) 你凌晨一点才回家 (he) You only came home at one in the morning
      " (e.g.) wǒmen xiàwǔ sì diǎn cái chī wǔfàn  (ph) 我们下午四点才吃午饭  (he) we don't have lunch until four o'clock in the afternoon / we only ate lunch at pm
      " (e.g.) wǒmen zuótiān cái rènshí (ph) 我们昨天才认识 (he) we only just met yesterday

